headline: Musk Vs. Buffett: Tesla CEO Goes 'Cancel Netflix,' While Oracle Of Omaha Streams Live Boxing
summary: Netflix Inc (NASDAQ:NFLX) released many hit shows and movies in the third quarter, but now faces the possibility of subscribers cancelling their memberships thanks to the world's richest person. But, while Elon Musk was telling people to cancel their Netflix memberships, another billionaire could provide a boost by supporting the company's live sports efforts.
